transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Islamuddin sir good afternoon.
Customer: Good afternoon ma'am.
Executive: Sir main Diksha baat karungi IndiaMART head office se kaise hain aap?
Customer: Bas badhiya.
Executive: Sir aapne abhi ek feedback diya hai that jo aapke sath video meeting hui thi you are not satisfied with that meeting.
Customer: Main ye bol raha hu ma'am na koi lead aa rahi hai ek bhi lead nahi uthai maine 10 mein.
Customer: Koi lead bhi tulsi pot ki aa rahi hai ma'am.
Executive: Iski tulsi pot ki lead aa rahi hai aap tulsi pot mein deal karte hain?
Customer: Ma'am itni budget kam aa raha hai na agar tulsi pot mein na karna only marble ka kar do ek kaam karo aap aise kar do na marble mandir ke kar do.
Executive: Ek minute rukiye ek minute ek minute rukiye.
Executive: Main open hi kar rahi hu aapka seller profile bhi.

Executive: Haan batayiye sir aapke paas aa rahi hai lead ek to stone garden planter planter ki vajah se aa rahi hai ek to lead.
Executive: Aur marble planter.
Customer: Ye sab hata do only mandir kar do aap ek kaam karo.
Executive: Aap ek baar aaiye seller open hai na abhi aapka?
Customer: Kya?
Executive: Seller panel aapne open kara hua hai na?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Products ko change kariye sir.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Aap dekhiye upar likhiye add product likha aa raha hoga na uske right mein search option aa raha hoga.
Executive: Add product likha aayega fir quick add aayega fir IM library aa raha hoga fir aa raha hoga pot.
Customer: Kya likha aa raha hai?
Executive: Ye add product aa raha hai quick add aa raha hai fir search box aa raha hoga ek.
Customer: Haan search aa raha hai.
Executive: Search aa raha hai na waha pe likhiye ek baar planter sirf plant bhi likhenge na to bhi chalega planter likhiye ek baar pehle.

Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Thik hai ab niche do aapke products aaye honge ek to marble carving planter aaya aur ek stone garden planter.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Ye dono hatane hai na aapko?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Dekhiye right mein three dots aa rahi hai.
Customer: Aa rahi hai.
Executive: Uspe uspe click karenge to deactivate ka option aayega.
Customer: Na wo to click karne ke baad mein aa rahi hai deactivate ka.
Executive: Haan haan deactivate karne ka haan.
Customer: Edit ka button hai.
Executive: Edit pe mat click kariye deactivate.
Customer: Edit ke button ke baad mein deactivate aa raha hai.
Executive: Haan bilkul sahi sir us deactivate pe hi click kar dijiye.
Customer: Haan ji wo product auto out of stock ho jayega in case future mein jab aapko lagta hai ki wo product ki lead aapko chahiye aap unhe activate bhi kar sakte hain.
Customer: Achcha achcha achcha niche stone garden planter aa raha hai use bhi deactivate kar dijiye isi tarike se.

Executive: Kar diya sir?
Customer: Haan kar diya jyadatar to kar diye carving den.
Executive: Thik hai iske baad sir aap aaiye right mein dekhiye ek option aa raha hai wahin pe jahan pe aapne plant likha tha waha pe ab aap likhiye tulsi.

Customer: Search mein tulsi aa gayi ma'am.
Executive: Bolo tulsi likha?
Customer: Haan likh diya ma'am.
Executive: Tulsi jab aap likhenge tab aap dekhiye ab tulsi wale tulsi planter wale aa gaye hain sare products.
Customer: Haan aa gaye ye ₹3300 ka ₹3300.
Customer: ₹3300 ₹3500.
Customer: Haan haan aa gaye.
Executive: Isi tarike se aap tulsi wale bhi aap sare out of stock kar liye.
Customer: Achcha do minute mein main na main kar lunga thoda customer hai na.
Executive: Thik hai sir aap ek baar main wait karu kyuki mujhe aapke sath aur bhi cheeze discuss karni thi na.
Customer: Thik hai thik hai thik hai.
Executive: Sir wo main ruk rahi hu aap customer se baat kariye.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai.
summary:
Concerns:

- Not getting relevant buyleads.

- Getting buyleads for Tulsi pots.

- Wants to remove marble and stone planters.



Resolution:

- Executive guided to remove marble and stone planters.

- Executive guided to search and remove tulsi planters.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will remove tulsi planters later.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- buyleads, subscription, product update, out of stock
